<topic template="Default" modified="2026-05-04T11:12:40.443+08:00" lasteditedby="noorhbo" version="2" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../helpproject.xsd" status="Needs Review">
  <title>工作选择屏幕</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading4">工作选择屏幕</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px;">在工件选择屏幕中，每个托盘最多可设置 10 个型号。</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px;">用于导航到工作屏幕,</para>
    <list id="0" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="%0:s)" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[MENU]</text>。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">显示主菜单。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">按下<text style="font-weight:bold;">[WORK]</text>图标。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">显示工作选择屏幕。</li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="" style="text-align:center; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:16px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:159px left ;"><image src="Work Selection Screen.png" imagestyleclass="Default" scale="28.00%" width="396" height="298" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="" style="text-align:center; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:159px left ;"><anchor id="Fig4.10" styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:11pt;"></anchor><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:11pt;">图 &lt;%HMFIGURECOUNTER3=4%&gt;.&lt;%HMFIGURECOUNTER%&gt;   工作选择</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;"> 屏幕</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px; page-break-before:always;"><text style="font-weight:bold;">项目说明</text></para>
    <list id="1" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="%0:s." format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px;"><text style="font-weight:bold;">NO. (工作模式编号)</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px;">最多可选择 10 个工作模式（模式 0 至 9）。按下相应的数字即可选择工件型号。所选型号将以黄色高亮显示。</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px;"><image src="Work model number.png" imagestyleclass="Default" scale="28.00%" width="279" height="89" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
    <list id="2" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="%0:s." format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="2" styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px;"><text style="font-weight:bold;">型号名称</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px;">型号名称用于方便识别，可在此输入。最多可输入 6 个字符作为型号名称。</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px;"><image src="Model name.png" imagestyleclass="Default" scale="30.00%" width="172" height="90" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
    <list id="3" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="%0:s." format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="3" styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px;"><text style="font-weight:bold;">PGM NO. [计划编号]</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px;">在此字段中输入各型号在自动循环中要执行的程序编号。有效范围为 1 至 7999。</para>
    <list id="4" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="%0:s." format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="4" styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px;"><text style="font-weight:bold;">空气座椅</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px;">在此字段中设置了需要对相应型号进行监控的气座。&apos; * &apos; 表示在夹具夹紧后检查传感器。要设置或重置，请使用<text style="font-weight:bold;">[SET]</text>或<text style="font-weight:bold;">[RESET]</text>软键。</para>
    <list id="5" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="%0:s." format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="5" styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px;"><text style="font-weight:bold;">打开检查模式</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px;">为了区分不同的型号，需要对座椅传感器进行型号检查。需要 &quot;开启&quot; 检查的传感器在此文件中设置。&apos; * &apos; 表示传感器已 &quot;开启&quot; 检查。要设置或重置，请使用<text style="font-weight:bold;">[SET]</text>或<text style="font-weight:bold;">[RESET]</text>软键。</para>
    <list id="6" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="%0:s." format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="6" styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px;"><text style="font-weight:bold;">模式关闭 检查</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px;">为了区分不同的型号，可通过座椅传感器进行型号检查。需要进行 &quot;关闭&quot; 检查的传感器在此字段中进行设置。&apos; * &apos; 表示传感器已 &quot;关闭&quot; 检查。要设置或重置，请使用<text style="font-weight:bold;">[SET]</text>或<text style="font-weight:bold;">[RESET]</text>软键。</para>
    <list id="7" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="%0:s." format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="7" styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px;"><text style="font-weight:bold;">A-RWH 职位</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal">夹具应在 RWH（旋转工作头）的哪个角度夹紧/松开，可根据各型号进行设置。</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px; page-break-before:always;"></para>
  </body>
</topic>
